        "name": "Danger — mutates data",
        "description": "Destructive / state-mutating requests only. Every request here inherits the folder's X-Yaak-Confirm header, whose prompt.text() forces a confirmation dialog on each send — cancel aborts the send. Entirely client-side (Yaak); the header is ignored by the server.",
